Package CAMs_App.entity

Class Student

java.lang.Object
CAMs_App.entity.User
CAMs_App.entity.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Student>
public class Student extends User implements Comparable<Student>
The Student class represents a student user in the system. It extends User class and includes additional information such as registered camps and points earned. Each student object has a corresponding CampComMem object.
